ngle Integration run might get lucky (LLM happens to align) while a retry would fail. Multiple runs (Agentic) would catch intermittent misalignment.\n\n**Key reasoning:**\n- Behaviors 1 & 3 are pure business logic → Unit level is sufficient\n- Behavior 2 & 5 depend on explanation quality → Agentic (if LLM-based) is safer\n- Behavior 4 is explicitly semantic → Agentic required"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":13532,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":13532},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"75ae1625-c2ea-45d8-aecc-2ecb6447ae58","uuid":"f58901a3-122f-4a83-a728-dff4446a24b1"}
